      "extra": {
        "message": "Missing rate limiting on /login endpoint\n\nThe /login endpoint has no rate limiting or account lockout mechanism. An attacker can make unlimited login attempts to brute-force credentials.\n\nImpact: An attacker can perform unlimited brute-force attacks against user accounts to discover valid credentials.\n\nFix: Implement rate limiting (e.g., Flask-Limiter) and account lockout after a number of failed attempts.",
